with access to airliners 
reorganizaton of the faa to give security operations higher 
status 
more research and development of devices to detect the most 
sophisticated terrorist bombs and of ways to reinforce airliners 
against damage from small explosions 
establishment of a system for letting passengers know when an 
airliner has received a credible bomb threat 
more humane procedures for dealing with victims of foreign 
terrorism and their family members 
